        <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </span>Sole Proprietorship, Partnership, Limited Liability Company
        (LLC), or Corporation; which one is right for me?&nbsp; Each has its
        advantages and disadvantages. Consult with the Law Office of Robert I.
        Long to find out which one is best for your circumstances. Already have
        a company?&nbsp; We can help with navigating the regulatory requirements.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>
